	<b>Purpose of the research:</b> To understand how you, your friends, and people we hire can use Mobi to plan itineraries for a day of a trip.
	<br/><br/>
	<b>What you will do in this research</b>: If you decide to participate, you will:
	<ul>
	  <li>Sign up by providing details on what you are looking for in this day trip. This is then given to your friends and people we hire, who will plan a day of your trip during the 
	    one-week period immediately after you sign up.</li>
	  <li>Recruit your friends to help plan your trip for you using Mobi.</li>
	  <li>Keep track of how the plans are coming along over the course of the week and make suggestions or changes as you see fit.</li>
	  <li>Review the two final itineraries and complete a followup survey.</li>
	</ul>
	<b>Time required</b>: About 10-15 minutes to sign up and about 20-25 minutes for
	the post-survey. A few minutes a day to check on how the itineraries are coming along.
	<br/><br/>
	<b>Benefits</b>: You get two custom-tailored itineraries as well as a collection of activities of potential interest. You will also receive a <b>$30 Amazon gift card</b> upon completing the followup survey!
	<br/><br/>
	<b>Confidentiality</b>: Data collected will contain personal identifiers, but no personal information will be shared publicly nor published.
	<br/><br/>
	<b>Participation and withdrawal</b>: Your participation is completely voluntary, and you may quit at any time without penalty.
	<br/><br/>
	<b>To Contact the Researcher</b>: If you have questions or concerns about this research, please contact:<br/>
